    def create_client_profile(self, client_id: str, base_config: dict) -> bool
```

**ĞŸÑ€Ğ¾Ğ¼Ğ¿Ñ‚ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Claude Code (Shopify Tool):**
```
Ğ—Ğ°Ğ´Ğ°Ñ‡Ğ°: Ğ¡Ñ‚Ğ²Ğ¾Ñ€Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¸ ProfileManager Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Shopify Tool Ğ½Ğ° Ğ¾ÑĞ½Ğ¾Ğ²Ñ– Packing Tool

