- Ğ‘Ğ°Ğ·Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ¸Ğ¹ ÑˆĞ»ÑÑ…: \\192.168.88.101\Z_GreenDelivery\WAREHOUSE\0UFulfilment
- Ğ¡Ñ‚Ñ€ÑƒĞºÑ‚ÑƒÑ€Ğ°: Clients/CLIENT_{ID}/shopify_config.json

