### 4.3 Code quality Ñ‚Ğ° linting

**ĞĞ°Ğ»Ğ°ÑˆÑ‚ÑƒĞ²Ğ°Ğ½Ğ½Ñ:**

1. **ruff.toml:**
```toml
line-length = 100
target-version = "py39"

[lint]
select = ["E", "F", "W", "I", "N"]
ignore = ["E501"]  # Line too long (handled by formatter)

[format]
quote-style = "double"
indent-style = "space"
```

2. **CI/CD setup** (GitHub Actions):
```yaml
name: Tests and Linting

on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: windows-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v2
        with:
          python-version: 3.9
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: pip install -r requirements-dev.txt
      - name: Run linter
        run: ruff check .
      - name: Run tests
        run: pytest --cov --cov-report=xml
      - name: Upload coverage
        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v2
```

**ĞŸÑ€Ğ¾Ğ¼Ğ¿Ñ‚ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Claude Code:**
```
Ğ—Ğ°Ğ´Ğ°Ñ‡Ğ°: ĞĞ°Ğ»Ğ°ÑˆÑ‚ÑƒĞ²Ğ°Ñ‚Ğ¸ code quality tools

Ğ ĞµĞ¿Ğ¾Ğ·Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¾Ñ€Ñ–Ğ¹: [Ğ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ´Ğ²Ğ°]

Ğ©Ğ¾ Ğ·Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¸:
1. Ğ¡Ñ‚Ğ²Ğ¾Ñ€Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¸ ruff.toml Ğ· Ğ½Ğ°Ğ»Ğ°ÑˆÑ‚ÑƒĞ²Ğ°Ğ½Ğ½ÑĞ¼Ğ¸
2. Ğ—Ğ°Ğ¿ÑƒÑÑ‚Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¸ ruff check . Ñ‚Ğ° Ğ²Ğ¸Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ°Ğ²Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğ¸ Ğ²ÑÑ– issues
